    | list<string> getDimensions()                   |
    | bool         renameDimension(string old_name,  |
    |                             string new_name)   |
    |                                                |
    | string       getName()                         |
    | dict<mixed>  getMetadata()                     |
    +------------------------------------------------+
                   |
                   +--------------------------------------------------------------+
